5
00:01:46,740 --> 00:01:48,240
What are you guys doing?

6
00:01:48,240 --> 00:01:50,200
Put it down!

7
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:52,870
What are you guys doing here?

8
00:01:52,870 --> 00:01:56,500
The inspection for the accepting of goods isn't completed yet, how can you unload the goods on your own already?

9
00:01:56,500 --> 00:01:59,150
Didn't we already check with your people?

10
00:01:59,150 --> 00:02:01,300
Who did you check with?

11
00:02:01,300 --> 00:02:02,780
Me.

12
00:02:04,460 --> 00:02:06,520
Why are you here?

13
00:02:07,960 --> 00:02:11,150
All eight carts of goods have been inspected fully.

14
00:02:11,150 --> 00:02:12,880
It's just that I have a question.

15
00:02:12,880 --> 00:02:15,840
Why do these eight carts of goods require so many people to escort?

16
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:18,290
I am only taking orders.

17
00:02:18,290 --> 00:02:19,980
If you have any doubts,

18
00:02:19,980 --> 00:02:22,430
just ask my superior, Adjutant Mo.

19
00:02:22,430 --> 00:02:25,320
- Then, may I ask where Adjutant Mo is?
- Pei Xingjian.

20
00:02:25,990 --> 00:02:29,960
You are only a scholar, can you have some respect?

21
00:02:30,870 --> 00:02:34,430
Everyone, listen well. Simen College's Director of Studies

22
00:02:34,430 --> 00:02:38,530
has appointed me to inspect the goods for acceptance. I am solely in charge here.

23
00:02:38,530 --> 00:02:40,570
No one can interfere.

24
00:02:41,470 --> 00:02:43,470
Understood?

25
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:47,390
- Yes.
- Where's your supervisor?

26
00:02:47,390 --> 00:02:50,890
Adjutant Mo got a stomach ache on the way over, so he went to the restroom.

27
00:02:50,890 --> 00:02:53,620
Look! Adjutant Mo is here.

28
00:03:05,930 --> 00:03:10,450
Good Brother Mo, I didn't expect to see you again so soon.

29
00:03:10,450 --> 00:03:13,430
I originally wanted to come and pay respects after I finished my tasks.

30
00:03:13,430 --> 00:03:16,250
Unexpectedly, I ran into Brother Pei.

31
00:03:16,250 --> 00:03:20,730
I just don't understand why you pretended not to know me in the storage room.

32
00:03:20,730 --> 00:03:24,100
Is there something wrong with the goods that I transported?

33
00:03:24,100 --> 00:03:25,740
Let me ask you.

34
00:03:25,740 --> 00:03:28,270
In the past, transporting the goods never needed assistance from the Ministry of War.

35
00:03:28,270 --> 00:03:30,210
Why is it such a big deal this time?

36
00:03:30,210 --> 00:03:32,530
About this, I also have asked many.

37
00:03:32,530 --> 00:03:34,560
But no one answered.

38
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:36,600
This is odd.

39
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:40,030
I inspected those eight carts of goods.

40
00:03:40,030 --> 00:03:43,470
Inside were just paper used by Simen College. Nothing seemed improper.

41
00:03:43,470 --> 00:03:47,230
Those eight carts were what was transported today. There will be another batch tomorrow.

42
00:03:47,230 --> 00:03:48,720
There's more tomorrow?

43
00:03:48,720 --> 00:03:51,010
The shipment this time has 20 carts in total.

44
00:03:51,010 --> 00:03:53,400
Another Adjutant and I are responsible for the transport.

45
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:55,700
There is one lot of goods among them that have been delayed for some reason.

46
00:03:55,700 --> 00:03:58,660
If there are no accidents, it'll arrive tomorrow.

47
00:03:58,660 --> 00:04:00,290
That's it.

48
00:04:00,290 --> 00:04:04,080
The problem is with the lot of goods that will arrive tomorrow.

49
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:08,810
Brother Pei, why are you so sure that there is a problem with this lot of goods?

50
00:04:08,810 --> 00:04:12,080
Xue Xu is someone who is greedy for fame and fortune.

51
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:14,900
He is always declining to do the work that he is supposed to do.

52
00:04:14,900 --> 00:04:17,170
This time, he just went to serve Prince of Cao,

53
00:04:17,170 --> 00:04:18,690
yet he volunteered to do.

54
00:04:18,690 --> 00:04:22,110
This inspection work requires effort in minute detail.

55
00:04:22,110 --> 00:04:24,950
There must be a secret within this.

56
00:04:24,950 --> 00:04:27,820
In that case, this matter is related to Prince of Cao.

57
00:04:27,820 --> 00:04:31,920
The crown prince has proposed to His Majesty to emphasize more on imperial scholars and less on classics comprehension

58
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:34,870
to promote reforming the imperial examination system. Prince of Cao thinks

59
00:04:34,870 --> 00:04:38,370
that the crown prince's reform will take on the privilege and benefits enjoyed by the aristocrats and nobles,

60
00:04:38,370 --> 00:04:40,950
and he is trying to block it.

61
00:04:40,950 --> 00:04:43,270
Now that he would even utilize the Ministry of War,

62
00:04:43,270 --> 00:04:45,980
he must be planning something big.

63
00:04:49,730 --> 00:04:53,150
Master, the artist from Ruyi Resist Dye Shop is here and wants to see you.

64
00:04:53,150 --> 00:04:55,980
So soon?

65
00:04:59,820 --> 00:05:03,850
Good Brother, have some tea first. I'll be right back.

66
00:05:08,320 --> 00:05:10,780
Hunting white rabbit in the spring, the ferocious tiger in the summer,

67
00:05:10,780 --> 00:05:13,680
fat deer in the autumn, and grey wolf in the winter.

68
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:15,740
These four paintings, when combined as one,

69
00:05:15,740 --> 00:05:18,500
can be made into the screen that Master Pei wants.

70
00:05:18,500 --> 00:05:21,960
Is Young Master Pei satisfied with these four paintings?

71
00:05:25,670 --> 00:05:28,760
I'm satisfied. They are even better than I had imagined.

72
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:31,820
And even faster in completion. Artist, you've worked hard.

73
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:35,410
May I ask Artist to make the screen

74
00:05:35,410 --> 00:05:37,460
with the image of these four paintings?

75
00:05:37,460 --> 00:05:40,780
The spirit of the original paintings must not be lost.

76
00:05:40,780 --> 00:05:42,990
I also want to thank Young Master Pei for giving me the medicine.

77
00:05:42,990 --> 00:05:45,030
If it weren't for this miraculous medicine given by Young Master Pei,

78
00:05:45,030 --> 00:05:47,320
my hand wouldn't have recovered so fast.

79
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:50,330
The paintings would have been charged with a discount then.

80
00:05:50,330 --> 00:05:51,810
Since Young Master Pei is satisfied,

81
00:05:51,810 --> 00:05:54,250
have I repaid all the favors that I owe you?

82
00:05:54,250 --> 00:05:59,780
You mean, the idea that I came up with to help you reject the marriage proposals?

83
00:06:00,990 --> 00:06:02,930
It's a trivial matter. Don't mention it.

84
00:06:02,930 --> 00:06:05,490
Artist, you don't need to worry about it too much.

85
00:06:05,490 --> 00:06:07,290
Young Master Pei, you don't have to be courteous.

86
00:06:07,290 --> 00:06:11,630
Just tell me if these four paintings are sufficient to repay your favors.

87
00:06:11,630 --> 00:06:13,820
Since Artist is asking so directly,

88
00:06:13,820 --> 00:06:16,430
I'll say they are about sufficient in repayment.

89
00:06:16,430 --> 00:06:17,530
Excellent.

90
00:06:17,530 --> 00:06:19,860
Since I have repaid everything that I should repay,

91
00:06:19,860 --> 00:06:23,610
then Young Master Pei, please pay me back what you should repay me.

92
00:06:29,420 --> 00:06:33,280
Artist, you were waiting for me here.

93
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:35,950
You saw it too, that

94
00:06:35,950 --> 00:06:38,570
I am not an impoverished person.

95
00:06:38,570 --> 00:06:41,350
Why would I take your cousin's things and not return them?

96
00:06:41,350 --> 00:06:43,540
This is exactly what I want to ask Young Master Pei.

97
00:06:43,540 --> 00:06:45,630
I am someone who takes a strong stand on benevolence and grievance.

98
00:06:45,630 --> 00:06:48,760
I repay benevolence with benevolence and grievance with a grievance.

99
00:06:51,530 --> 00:06:53,590
If Young Master Pei insists on not returning those things,

100
00:06:53,590 --> 00:06:56,580
this artist knows how to find a way to get them back.

101
00:06:56,580 --> 00:06:59,020
At that time, I'm afraid our harmony will be hurt.

102
00:06:59,020 --> 00:07:02,670
Young Master Pei will actually resent me for burning the bridge after crossing the river.

103
00:07:03,580 --> 00:07:05,230
What do you mean by that?

104
00:07:05,230 --> 00:07:08,870
I'm very clear with what I said.

105
00:07:08,870 --> 00:07:11,280
Give me back my things, or you'll suffer the consequences.

106
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:15,000
You... are really a smart person who gets muddled sometimes.

107
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:17,550
I already told you that I didn't take your cousin's things.

108
00:07:17,550 --> 00:07:19,760
How can I return them to you?

109
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:21,880
I have already been as kind and dutiful as I could.

110
00:07:21,880 --> 00:07:25,080
It's needless to talk more. Goodbye!

111
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,550
[Simen College]

112
00:07:46,430 --> 00:07:48,950
This civilian woman Yu'er greets Lord Xue.

113
00:07:49,670 --> 00:07:52,640
I have a grievance and would like to ask Lord Xue to uphold justice.

114
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:56,500
This is not the magistrate's office. I don't have the time to accommodate you.

115
00:08:02,050 --> 00:08:03,830
This is not the magistrate's office.

116
00:08:03,830 --> 00:08:05,960
How can I uphold justice for you?

117
00:08:05,960 --> 00:08:07,700
Lord Xue, don't you remember me, Yu'er?

118
00:08:07,700 --> 00:08:09,920
Last time you said you would help me

119
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:12,530
to get justice from Pei Xingjian.

120
00:08:20,100 --> 00:08:21,380
I remember it now.

121
00:08:21,380 --> 00:08:25,230
See, I didn't recognize you without your facial covering.

122
00:08:25,230 --> 00:08:27,440
It's me who has bothered you, Lord Xue.

123
00:08:27,440 --> 00:08:31,000
This is my plea. Please help me, Lord Xue,

124
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:33,190
to get my cousin's remaining items back.

125
00:08:33,190 --> 00:08:34,580
Little Lady, rest assured.

126
00:08:34,580 --> 00:08:38,750
This official has always found thieving rascals like Pei Xingjian.

127
00:08:38,750 --> 00:08:41,010
Don't be impatient. Just go home and wait for the news.

128
00:08:41,010 --> 00:08:43,530
This official will definitely get justice for you.

129
00:08:43,530 --> 00:08:45,410
Thank you.

130
00:08:54,860 --> 00:08:57,330
Pei Xingjian, Pei Xingjian.

131
00:08:57,330 --> 00:08:59,710
I was just needing a way to deal with you.

132
00:08:59,710 --> 00:09:01,860
Good.

133
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:29,330
This...

134
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:33,230
This way, please.

135
00:09:34,510 --> 00:09:37,580
Shopkeeper Shih, come this way, please.

136
00:09:43,910 --> 00:09:46,320
Please sit.

137
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:49,560
Madam Cao, I heard that your nephew

138
00:09:49,560 --> 00:09:52,910
likes that shopkeeper, A'Ni, at Ruyi Resist Dye Shop.

139
00:09:52,910 --> 00:09:57,310
He even helped her win the top prize at the Hu Merchants Fair.

140
00:09:57,310 --> 00:10:00,490
Is this true?

141
00:10:00,490 --> 00:10:02,870
Our family's dirty laundry has spread so quickly

142
00:10:02,870 --> 00:10:05,400
to Shopkeeper Shih?

143
00:10:06,560 --> 00:10:09,980
If it weren't for this matter, why would I go for this secondary plan?

144
00:10:09,990 --> 00:10:12,550
So that's how it is. Just as I thought.

145
00:10:12,550 --> 00:10:16,090
With your Caoji's strength, why would you use this method

146
00:10:16,090 --> 00:10:19,210
to deal with Ruyi Resist Dye Shop?

147
00:10:19,210 --> 00:10:21,850
That matter that I asked Shopkeeper Shih about last time,

148
00:10:21,850 --> 00:10:23,950
can you guarantee it fully?

149
00:10:23,950 --> 00:10:26,150
This business fair held by the Hu Merchants

150
00:10:26,150 --> 00:10:30,200
is for getting the best clothes to ship to the western region to sell.

151
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:33,530
At that time, it's not only the design that will be competed on,

152
00:10:33,530 --> 00:10:36,140
even more important is the quality.

153
00:10:36,140 --> 00:10:38,750
They will test whether the sample dress

154
00:10:38,750 --> 00:10:41,650
will fade and change shape after getting wet.

155
00:10:41,650 --> 00:10:43,750
The fabric used by Ruyi Resist Dye Shop

156
00:10:43,750 --> 00:10:48,410
has already been through processing to prevent fading and shrinkage. It's a high-quality fabric.

157
00:10:48,410 --> 00:10:50,350
This is not a problem.

158
00:10:50,350 --> 00:10:54,650
I deliberately gave unprocessed materials to A'Ni this time.

159
00:10:54,650 --> 00:10:57,280
No matter how beautiful a dress she makes,

160
00:10:57,280 --> 00:11:01,500
it will definitely lose.

161
00:11:01,500 --> 00:11:03,010
Excellent!

162
00:11:03,010 --> 00:11:05,790
I'll remember Shopkeeoer Shih's favor.

163
00:11:05,790 --> 00:11:09,420
Please have some fragrant tea and sit for a moment.

164
00:11:33,180 --> 00:11:36,320
Shopkeeper Shih, this is a little token of appreciation from Caoji.

165
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:38,960
You must accept it.

166
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:42,020
Then... I won't be impolite.

167
00:12:06,170 --> 00:12:08,570
Helper to outsiders,

168
00:12:08,570 --> 00:12:11,950
are you going to tip off Ruyi Resist Dye Shop?

169
00:12:11,950 --> 00:12:16,110
Auntie, you are utilizing some sneaky tricks.

170
00:12:16,110 --> 00:12:18,700
I am helping what's right over family ties.

171
00:12:18,700 --> 00:12:23,110
I won't stop you this time, but you'd better think it over.

172
00:12:23,110 --> 00:12:25,560
If you really want to marry A'Ni,

173
00:12:25,560 --> 00:12:28,190
you can't go and tell them.

174
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:32,850
Why not?

175
00:12:32,850 --> 00:12:35,200
When I went there to propose marriage for you,

176
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:39,690
A'Ni was very arrogant and simply looked down on you.

177
00:12:40,370 --> 00:12:43,670
Someone like A'Ni is very competitive.

178
00:12:43,670 --> 00:12:47,540
She is trying her best to win over us at the Hu Merchants Fair

179
00:12:47,540 --> 00:12:50,740
to help Ruyi Resist Dye Shop show off.

180
00:12:52,550 --> 00:12:57,460
This kind of woman, the more softhearted you are, the more she looks down at you.

181
00:12:57,460 --> 00:13:01,040
She will only look up at you if you win over her.

182
00:13:01,650 --> 00:13:03,740
If Caoji can get the contracts

183
00:13:03,740 --> 00:13:06,810
from the Hu merchants, we will be the leader in this business,

184
00:13:06,810 --> 00:13:08,920
and you will be a successful entrepreneur.

185
00:13:08,920 --> 00:13:13,140
She will then see you in her eyes and will be willing to marry you.

186
00:13:16,640 --> 00:13:19,290
I've said everything I should say.

187
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:24,160
Whether you want to tell them or not,

188
00:13:25,700 --> 00:13:28,240
you decide.

189
00:14:01,460 --> 00:14:05,680
This kind of woman, the more softhearted you are, the more she looks down at you.

190
00:14:05,680 --> 00:14:09,360
She will only look up at you if you win over her.

191
00:14:10,150 --> 00:14:15,240
If Caoji can get the contracts from the Hu merchants, we will be the leader in this business,

192
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:17,300
and you will be a successful entrepreneur.

193
00:14:17,300 --> 00:14:21,630
She will then see you in her eyes and will be willing to marry you.

194
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:39,680
A'Ni! A'Ni!

195
00:14:42,470 --> 00:14:44,130
A'Ni!

196
00:14:44,630 --> 00:14:46,830
A'Ni. A'Ni.

197
00:14:46,830 --> 00:14:50,680
Listen. Isn't there some sound coming from the outside?

198
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:56,240
A'Ni! A'Ni!

199
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:59,920
- Who is that?
- It's me, Cao Wu.

200
00:14:59,920 --> 00:15:01,960
Cao Wu?

201
00:15:01,960 --> 00:15:04,500
It's late, what are you doing here?

202
00:15:04,500 --> 00:15:08,350
I came to tell you that there is a problem with the fabric for your sample dress.

203
00:15:08,350 --> 00:15:10,100
Tomorrow is the Hu Merchants' Fair.

204
00:15:10,100 --> 00:15:12,830
You must be careful.

205
00:15:22,560 --> 00:15:26,980
We're doomed. We're totally doomed.

206
00:15:41,900 --> 00:15:45,070
A'Ni, it's useless to panic now.

207
00:15:45,070 --> 00:15:47,780
Why not think about a solution?

208
00:15:47,780 --> 00:15:51,790
From choosing the fabric, deciding on the color, to design,

209
00:15:51,790 --> 00:15:55,290
this dress took me a whole month to do.

210
00:15:55,290 --> 00:15:58,770
But now, there are only a few hours before sunrise.

211
00:15:58,770 --> 00:16:02,600
What solution can there be?

212
00:16:08,130 --> 00:16:11,970
This dress has already shrunk and set its shape.

213
00:16:11,970 --> 00:16:14,550
The colors are smeared, too.

214
00:16:15,630 --> 00:16:18,000
We might as well change this one.

215
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:19,810
As long as the design is good,

216
00:16:19,810 --> 00:16:22,250
we won't be afraid of the water test again.

217
00:16:22,250 --> 00:16:24,140
Change this one?

218
00:16:24,140 --> 00:16:28,120
How is it different from a reject right now?

219
00:16:28,750 --> 00:16:31,710
It takes effort to achieve. Since it's not at the last moment,

220
00:16:31,710 --> 00:16:33,810
why don't we try our best?

221
00:17:20,600 --> 00:17:22,460
Don't worry.

222
00:18:23,600 --> 00:18:27,020
[An Residence]

223
00:18:29,340 --> 00:18:31,630
Come! Come!

224
00:18:31,630 --> 00:18:34,240
[An Residence]

225
00:19:27,480 --> 00:19:31,520
Liuli. Liuli.

226
00:19:35,150 --> 00:19:38,780
You must be exhausted. Go sleep in the bed for a while.

227
00:19:40,970 --> 00:19:42,720
A'Ni.

228
00:19:45,710 --> 00:19:49,510
A'Ni, look!  How does this dress look?

229
00:19:53,320 --> 00:19:55,070
It's pretty.

230
00:19:55,840 --> 00:19:59,790
This is the first time that I've seen anyone who can make a skirt look like a flower.

231
00:19:59,790 --> 00:20:02,210
Red with a tinge of pink, beautiful and alluring,

232
00:20:02,210 --> 00:20:04,330
just like a peony flower.

233
00:20:05,260 --> 00:20:08,960
Liuli, you really worked hard.

234
00:20:08,960 --> 00:20:13,550
In just six hours, you made a new skirt.

235
00:20:14,120 --> 00:20:16,670
A'Ni, don't be too worried.

236
00:20:16,670 --> 00:20:19,790
Even though this skirt doesn't look as opulent and poised,

237
00:20:19,790 --> 00:20:22,450
but it looks more lively when worn now.

238
00:20:22,450 --> 00:20:24,820
More lively when worn?

239
00:20:24,820 --> 00:20:26,740
You just wait and see.

240
00:20:26,740 --> 00:20:29,740
Even if this dress won't get the Hu merchants' orders,

241
00:20:29,740 --> 00:20:33,730
it can still boost our Ruyi Resist Dye Shop's reputation.

242
00:20:52,870 --> 00:20:55,070
So early?

243
00:20:55,070 --> 00:20:56,960
The goods for today have already been stored?

244
00:20:56,960 --> 00:20:59,250
Young Master Pei.

245
00:20:59,250 --> 00:21:03,240
Early this morning when the sun just started shining, Assistant Professor Xue brought people over already.

246
00:21:04,170 --> 00:21:05,770
All twelve carts are already stored inside?

247
00:21:05,770 --> 00:21:09,820
It's 20 carts.

248
00:21:09,820 --> 00:21:12,280
Why eight extra carts?

249
00:21:12,920 --> 00:21:15,860
Wait! Let me go take a look inside.

