00:21:17,260 --> 00:21:20,730
no one is allowed into the forbidden storage room.

252
00:21:23,840 --> 00:21:26,090
I lost a jade pendant yesterday.

253
00:21:26,090 --> 00:21:28,230
It was passed down from my ancestors.

254
00:21:28,230 --> 00:21:33,000
I thought back carefully. It may have been dropped inside the storage room.

255
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:36,340
Just let me go inside to take a look. I can tell right away.

256
00:21:36,930 --> 00:21:38,970
All right then, I'll wait right here.

257
00:21:38,970 --> 00:21:40,710
Hurry.

258
00:21:40,710 --> 00:21:42,700
I'll go in and come right back.

259
00:21:45,840 --> 00:21:47,600
Thank you so much.

260
00:22:08,070 --> 00:22:10,230
Have you found it?

261
00:22:10,230 --> 00:22:12,780
I'm looking; I'll be ready soon.

262
00:22:29,390 --> 00:22:31,410
[Seal Date]

263
00:22:41,860 --> 00:22:45,030
How are these paper rolls? It's leather.

264
00:22:50,740 --> 00:22:54,720
Guards! Arrest Pei Xingjian!

265
00:22:56,310 --> 00:22:58,750
Xue Xu, what are you arresting me for?

266
00:22:58,750 --> 00:23:01,320
The crown prince is just carrying out a reform for the imperial examination.

267
00:23:01,320 --> 00:23:03,940
He gave out orders to keep the Imperial Academy under strict control.

268
00:23:03,940 --> 00:23:06,490
This is the repertory place of four schools of the Imperial Academy.

269
00:23:06,490 --> 00:23:08,170
It is strictly forbidden for people who waste their time with trivial matters to enter here.

270
00:23:08,170 --> 00:23:11,050
- Did you maybe not know that?
- Absurd!

271
00:23:11,050 --> 00:23:14,060
I am a student of these four schools. How do I spend my time with trivial matters?

272
00:23:14,060 --> 00:23:16,720
Besides, I didn't look through the merchandise.

273
00:23:16,720 --> 00:23:18,420
If you don't believe me, open those boxes and see for yourself.

274
00:23:18,420 --> 00:23:20,540
See what's really in there.

275
00:23:20,540 --> 00:23:22,220
All right.

276
00:23:22,220 --> 00:23:25,400
You are getting smart with me and even denying it.

277
00:23:25,400 --> 00:23:28,800
An ordinary woman called Yu'er has filed a lawsuit against Pei Xingjian.

278
00:23:28,800 --> 00:23:32,730
He misappropriated a huge amount of goods.

279
00:23:32,730 --> 00:23:35,510
As signed by Simen College's Director of Studies.

280
00:23:35,510 --> 00:23:40,410
Effective immediately, Pei Xingjian is suspended until further investigation.

281
00:23:40,410 --> 00:23:42,430
You are such a muddled artist.

282
00:23:42,430 --> 00:23:45,390
Aren't you causing trouble for me?

283
00:23:45,390 --> 00:23:47,190
Carry him out!

284
00:23:48,580 --> 00:23:50,330
No need.

285
00:23:51,130 --> 00:23:53,210
I can walk.

286
00:24:08,960 --> 00:24:11,100
Is anyone there?

287
00:24:13,210 --> 00:24:16,230
[An Residence]

288
00:24:19,300 --> 00:24:21,740
You... Who are you looking for?

289
00:24:30,160 --> 00:24:35,280
I'm Pei Xingjian. I'm looking for an artist called Yu'er.

290
00:24:35,280 --> 00:24:37,930
You're not looking for A'Ni.

291
00:24:37,930 --> 00:24:40,440
Yu'er. These past few days,

292
00:24:40,440 --> 00:24:43,330
there really has been a young woman going in and out with A'Ni.

293
00:24:43,330 --> 00:24:46,630
They've gone to the Hu Merchants Fair in the Western Market since early this morning.

294
00:24:47,850 --> 00:24:50,950
- Hu Merchants Fair?
- I was just about to go to the Western Market to find A'Ni.

295
00:24:50,950 --> 00:24:53,850
If you have an urgent matter, why not just go with me?

296
00:24:53,850 --> 00:24:56,910
- Okay. Thanks.
- Let's go.

297
00:25:10,240 --> 00:25:14,640
[Western Market]

298
00:25:23,920 --> 00:25:27,020
[Hu Merchants Fair]

299
00:25:33,720 --> 00:25:37,910
[Hu Market]

300
00:26:08,330 --> 00:26:10,310
- Here!
- I want it!

301
00:26:10,310 --> 00:26:14,100
Me, too!

302
00:27:19,710 --> 00:27:21,790
[Ruyi]

303
00:27:21,790 --> 00:27:25,590
I had no idea that Ruyi Resist Dye's reputation would be so high in the dressmaking business.

304
00:27:25,590 --> 00:27:28,620
It's all thanks to Attire Expert An leaving us a peerless craft in dyeing fabrics.

305
00:27:28,620 --> 00:27:31,810
That's how Ruyi Resist Dye Shop has a good reputation.

306
00:27:45,210 --> 00:27:47,080
What are you looking for?

307
00:27:47,080 --> 00:27:49,540
I think I saw that bad guy.

308
00:27:59,030 --> 00:28:01,270
Release me! You...

309
00:28:01,270 --> 00:28:05,300
You have just a little bit of martial art skill and you bully me.

310
00:28:05,300 --> 00:28:08,740
Tell me. What good have you done?

311
00:28:08,740 --> 00:28:11,020
Mister Pei, let's talk it out.

312
00:28:11,020 --> 00:28:13,660
Release Yu'er first.

313
00:28:13,660 --> 00:28:17,670
If Miss Yu'er withdraws the lawsuit that falsely accuses me and exonerates me,

314
00:28:17,670 --> 00:28:20,340
I will definitely release her acupoint.

315
00:28:24,780 --> 00:28:28,310
A'Ni, I didn't sleep all night, so I'm really sleepy now.

316
00:28:28,310 --> 00:28:30,860
I was just worrying that there wasn't anywhere to nap.

317
00:28:30,860 --> 00:28:33,550
Now it's all good. Thank you for fulfilling my wishes.

318
00:28:33,550 --> 00:28:36,210
Even while standing, I can take a sound nap.

319
00:28:36,210 --> 00:28:40,210
When your superior checks again, there will be an extra suit against your bullying a civilian woman.

320
00:28:40,210 --> 00:28:43,400
- It really kills two birds with the same stone.
- Youâ€”

321
00:28:53,670 --> 00:28:56,180
I always thought you were a bit strange.

322
00:28:56,180 --> 00:28:58,440
I just remembered it.

323
00:28:59,430 --> 00:29:03,280
You said previously that you like your cousin.

324
00:29:03,280 --> 00:29:08,380
For your cousin, you would rather never marry.

325
00:29:08,380 --> 00:29:10,950
Yet soon after your cousin died,

326
00:29:10,950 --> 00:29:13,890
I don't see a trace of sadness in you.

327
00:29:13,890 --> 00:29:17,070
Yet, you're prettied up like a flower

328
00:29:17,070 --> 00:29:20,630
and enthusiastically going to attend the Hu Merchants Fair.

329
00:29:20,630 --> 00:29:23,850
This just doesn't make sense, does it?

330
00:29:28,750 --> 00:29:31,980
My... My stomach hurts.

331
00:29:31,980 --> 00:29:33,820
What trick are you playing now?

332
00:29:33,820 --> 00:29:35,820
Young Master Pei, please release Yu'er first.

333
00:29:35,820 --> 00:29:39,560
Ruyi Resist Dye Shop is willing to guarantee for Yu'er.

334
00:29:39,560 --> 00:29:42,220
This artist Yu'er is cunning and clever.

335
00:29:42,220 --> 00:29:44,570
What if she runs away?

336
00:29:46,200 --> 00:29:49,650
Young Master Pei, you're overthinking. This matter, even if you don't go and find her,

337
00:29:49,650 --> 00:29:53,780
she will go to you to get her possessions back. How can she run away?

338
00:29:53,780 --> 00:29:56,380
Why must you use martial arts to constrain a delicate girl?

339
00:29:56,380 --> 00:30:00,910
If people heard about it, I'm afraid it wouldn't sound too good to anyone.

340
00:30:00,910 --> 00:30:02,850
That's right!

341
00:30:08,350 --> 00:30:10,570
You hit me?

342
00:30:16,560 --> 00:30:19,580
A'Ni, my stomach hurts. I need to go to the restroom.

343
00:30:19,580 --> 00:30:21,510
Hurry and go.

344
00:30:33,940 --> 00:30:35,970
Come! Come!

345
00:30:41,520 --> 00:30:43,230
I got it!

346
00:31:00,950 --> 00:31:04,400
Oh no! I forgot to give the clothes to A'Ni.

347
00:31:10,130 --> 00:31:12,610
Little brother, I have a bag here.

348
00:31:12,610 --> 00:31:15,840
If you help me take it backstage to Shopkeeper A'Ni of the Ruyi Resist Dye Shop,

349
00:31:15,840 --> 00:31:18,830
- I will buy a dough figure for you. All right?
- Yes, yes!

350
00:31:18,830 --> 00:31:22,820
Okay, it's this bundle. Carry it well.

351
00:31:27,470 --> 00:31:29,740
- Youâ€”
- Your stomach doesn't hurt anymore?

352
00:31:31,130 --> 00:31:32,630
It's such an important bundle.

353
00:31:32,630 --> 00:31:35,140
It'll be safer with me.

354
00:31:42,660 --> 00:31:45,500
Older Sister, the dough figure?

355
00:31:48,550 --> 00:31:50,700
Hurry up and buy him a dough figure.

356
00:31:50,700 --> 00:31:53,990
- Why should I buy it?
- Of course you should. You stole his business.

357
00:31:53,990 --> 00:31:57,040
Besides, haven't all my riches been conned away by you?

358
00:31:57,040 --> 00:31:58,370
Youâ€”

359
00:32:13,370 --> 00:32:17,340
- Boss, give me a dough figure.
- Yes.

360
00:32:20,270 --> 00:32:22,080
Which one do you want?

361
00:32:22,710 --> 00:32:24,580
[Suguard Dough Figures]

362
00:32:30,160 --> 00:32:34,360
Here. Next time you meet a stranger, you can't interact with them.

363
00:32:34,360 --> 00:32:36,640
Thank you.

364
00:32:40,720 --> 00:32:42,820
Buy one for me, too.

365
00:32:43,490 --> 00:32:46,840
You never did anything good. Why should I buy one for you?

366
00:32:58,150 --> 00:33:00,990
- I didn't take your things.
- I didn't falsely accuse a good person.

367
00:33:00,990 --> 00:33:03,290
- Then withdraw the lawsuit.
- Then give me my things back.

368
00:33:03,290 --> 00:33:05,950
If you withdraw the lawsuit, I'll give you those things back.

369
00:33:05,950 --> 00:33:08,110
No, that's not right. I got dizzy because of you.

370
00:33:08,110 --> 00:33:10,750
How many times have I told you? I didn't take your stuff.

371
00:33:10,750 --> 00:33:13,910
Go to Simen College and withdraw the lawsuit.

372
00:33:13,910 --> 00:33:17,430
If you don't return the things, I won't withdraw it.

373
00:33:18,200 --> 00:33:21,350
- What good does it do me to lie to you?
- Are you returning or not?

374
00:33:21,350 --> 00:33:23,950
I really didn't take your stuff.

375
00:33:26,900 --> 00:33:28,700
Who are you?

376
00:33:30,440 --> 00:33:32,570
This time's fair was organized by us.

377
00:33:32,570 --> 00:33:35,210
Because there are more shops participating than we expected,

378
00:33:35,210 --> 00:33:38,830
so we're going to take the shops' sample backstage to pre-register.

379
00:33:38,830 --> 00:33:43,820
This way, we'll have sufficient time to analyze the samples' quality and design.

380
00:33:43,820 --> 00:33:46,950
You've really thought it through. Then I'll leave it to you.

381
00:33:46,950 --> 00:33:48,480
Give it to me.

382
00:33:52,330 --> 00:33:53,630
I'm warning you.

383
00:33:53,630 --> 00:33:55,700
Don't have any ideas on this sample dress.

384
00:33:55,700 --> 00:33:58,950
This fair is very important to our Ruyi Resist Dye Shop.

385
00:33:58,950 --> 00:34:02,260
You can pick on me, but you can't make it hard for others!

386
00:34:09,400 --> 00:34:13,120
This is Ruyi Resist Dye Shop's. Don't forget.

387
00:34:13,120 --> 00:34:15,560
I won't forget. Please rest assured.

388
00:34:15,560 --> 00:34:17,320
Thank you.

389
00:34:28,620 --> 00:34:31,470
Laughable, laughable.

390
00:34:31,470 --> 00:34:33,760
What do you mean by this?

391
00:34:35,380 --> 00:34:39,060
Did you really not notice? He's not some Hu merchant at all.

392
00:34:39,060 --> 00:34:40,490
What are you saying?

393
00:34:40,490 --> 00:34:41,860
Look at you.

394
00:34:41,860 --> 00:34:45,420
You have a smart face, yet you're so dumb.

395
00:34:45,420 --> 00:34:50,430
Not only can you not recognize who stole your stuff, but you also gave your sample to a con man.

396
00:34:50,430 --> 00:34:53,820
I really worry about Ruyi Resist Dye Shop.

397
00:34:53,820 --> 00:34:56,570
You... You're lying!

398
00:34:56,570 --> 00:34:59,550
If you don't believe me, you can ask other embroidery shops.

399
00:34:59,550 --> 00:35:01,930
Ask them if they turned in their samples.

400
00:35:09,550 --> 00:35:12,420
But even if you ask now, you'll be wasting your time.

401
00:35:12,420 --> 00:35:14,060
How about this.

402
00:35:14,970 --> 00:35:18,060
Go to Simen College and withdraw your lawsuit that falsely accuses me.

403
00:35:18,060 --> 00:35:21,470
I'll help you chase down your sample. How about that?

404
00:35:22,630 --> 00:35:27,080
Don't you dare try to trick me! Whether or not he is a swindler, I will know once I go to the back.

405
00:35:28,970 --> 00:35:32,650
Hey! If you don't go after him, it'll be too late!

406
00:35:33,580 --> 00:35:36,210
- Can you help me over here?
- Okay.

407
00:35:36,210 --> 00:35:38,240
Have you sorted things out?

408
00:35:38,240 --> 00:35:39,860
We need to check it.

409
00:35:39,860 --> 00:35:42,610
Smoothen it out again.

410
00:35:42,610 --> 00:35:45,170
- Don't be nervous.
- It's not even.

411
00:36:01,830 --> 00:36:05,970
Great!

412
00:36:16,270 --> 00:36:19,690
Honored friends of Great Tang,

413
00:36:19,690 --> 00:36:21,510
are you well?

414
00:36:21,510 --> 00:36:24,370
We're good!

415
00:36:24,890 --> 00:36:28,370
My name is Cao Lushan. My tribesmen and friends

416
00:36:28,370 --> 00:36:30,870
came from the west of the faraway Cong Mountains,
(Today's Pamir Mountains)

417
00:36:30,870 --> 00:36:33,020
the vast western region.

418
00:36:33,020 --> 00:36:36,190
We crossed many moutains and rivers to come to Chang'an

419
00:36:36,190 --> 00:36:39,100
so that we can take Chang'an's bustle and riches

420
00:36:39,100 --> 00:36:41,710
to bring it back to our home.

421
00:36:41,710 --> 00:36:45,290
Today, we want to pick the most

422
00:36:45,290 --> 00:36:47,450
beautiful clothing in Changan.

423
00:36:47,450 --> 00:36:50,950
Hurry up and check carefully, don't let there be any problems.

424
00:36:50,950 --> 00:36:53,720
The business that gets ranked the highest

425
00:36:53,720 --> 00:36:56,830
will not only enjoy a one-year contract with the western region,

426
00:36:56,830 --> 00:37:00,960
but will also become the king of business

427
00:37:00,960 --> 00:37:02,780
to the Hu merchants!

428
00:37:02,780 --> 00:37:05,690
Great!

429
00:37:05,690 --> 00:37:10,460
The dressmaking competition starts now!

430
00:37:14,160 --> 00:37:17,960
#1 and #2 go on stage.

431
00:37:17,960 --> 00:37:20,200
#3 and #4 prepare.

432
00:37:20,200 --> 00:37:21,310
Hurry, hurry!  We are next.

433
00:37:21,310 --> 00:37:23,920
Good Brother, sorry to bother you,

434
00:37:23,920 --> 00:37:26,300
can you still change the order to go on stage?

435
00:37:26,300 --> 00:37:28,760
We, Ruyi Resist Dye Shop want to be further back.

436
00:37:28,760 --> 00:37:31,490
- This--
- No way!

437
00:37:31,490 --> 00:37:34,650
The order was chosen from drawing sticks between so many businesses.

438
00:37:34,650 --> 00:37:37,520
Why can you guys change whenever you guys like?

439
00:37:37,520 --> 00:37:39,210
- That is not fair!
- Exactly!

440
00:37:39,210 --> 00:37:42,200
Exactly! That is not fair.

441
00:37:42,200 --> 00:37:45,560
- On what basis? We're all here to compete.
- That's right.

442
00:37:45,560 --> 00:37:47,980
I'm sorry, Shopkeeper A'Ni.

443
00:37:47,980 --> 00:37:51,720
The rules are already set. They can't be easily changed.

444
00:37:51,720 --> 00:37:54,220
Please help out.

445
00:37:55,200 --> 00:37:57,320
A'Ni!

446
00:37:57,320 --> 00:37:58,300
[Ruyi]

447
00:37:58,300 --> 00:38:00,240
- A'Ni.
- Let's go.

448
00:38:02,210 --> 00:38:05,300
Why are you back just now? The competition has already started.

449
00:38:05,300 --> 00:38:07,430
Hurry up and give me the clothing.

450
00:38:11,330 --> 00:38:14,200
Come back!  You cannot go.

451
00:38:14,200 --> 00:38:15,530
It hurts! Auntie!

452
00:38:15,530 --> 00:38:17,390
Where's the clothing?

453
00:38:17,390 --> 00:38:18,800
What happened?

454
00:38:18,800 --> 00:38:20,690
I think I was scammed.

455
00:38:20,690 --> 00:38:23,270
Just now, a man told me that he was from the Hu Merchant Fair

456
00:38:23,270 --> 00:38:24,650
and needed to take the sample dress first.

457
00:38:24,650 --> 00:38:26,930
I really believed it.

458
00:38:33,590 --> 00:38:36,290
It must be Caoji's trick. I'll go deal with them.

459
00:38:36,290 --> 00:38:37,770
Wait.

460
00:38:37,770 --> 00:38:40,450
We don't have proof. We cannot accuse them.

461
00:38:40,450 --> 00:38:43,110
If we do, people will make use of it.

462
00:38:44,890 --> 00:38:48,770
Then what should we do? Do we really just leave it?

463
00:38:50,960 --> 00:38:56,770
Here are the clothes made by Wangji Shop and Gaoji Shop.

464
00:39:04,840 --> 00:39:08,810
Without the clothing, how do we attend the competition?

465
00:39:11,850 --> 00:39:15,960
A'Ni, don't get worried yet. Let's wait a bit.

466
00:39:15,960 --> 00:39:17,620
Wait for Pei Xingjian.

467
00:39:17,620 --> 00:39:19,750
Pei Xingjian?

468
00:40:08,950 --> 00:40:11,160
#9 Caoji Resist Dye Shop is up.

469
00:40:11,160 --> 00:40:13,610
Mother, hurry! Hurry!

470
00:40:13,610 --> 00:40:16,440
#10 Ruyi Resist Dye Shop is up.

471
00:40:18,980 --> 00:40:21,280
Caoji is coming.

472
00:40:33,480 --> 00:40:35,510
- Wow!
- Yes.

473
00:40:35,510 --> 00:40:37,430
Wow!

474
00:40:37,430 --> 00:40:39,410
Beautiful!

475
00:40:52,480 --> 00:40:56,390
A'Ni. Sorry.

476
00:40:56,430 --> 00:41:00,290
How can I blame you? It is Caoji's fault.

477
00:41:00,290 --> 00:41:04,500
If it weren't for you, Ruyi Resist Dye Shop wouldn't even have a second sample dress.

478
00:41:08,670 --> 00:41:11,810
This is the sample dress of our Caoji Resist Dye Shop.

479
00:41:11,810 --> 00:41:14,150
We used the best cloth

480
00:41:14,150 --> 00:41:16,810
and the most fantastic skills

481
00:41:16,810 --> 00:41:20,640
to represent Great Tang's highest level of dressmaking skills.

482
00:41:20,640 --> 00:41:24,670
Our Caoji Resist Dye Shop is the Number One Needle in the World.

483
00:41:24,670 --> 00:41:27,390
There is only one in the world.

484
00:41:29,700 --> 00:41:33,310
A'Ni, why have you still not prepared to go up?

485
00:41:37,450 --> 00:41:41,980
I am really sorry. Ruyi Resist Dye Shop's clothing has gone missing.

486
00:41:41,980 --> 00:41:44,040
We can only withdraw from the fair.

487
00:42:32,720 --> 00:42:34,460
What are you doing?

488
00:42:34,460 --> 00:42:36,730
Yes, what's happening?

489
00:42:36,730 --> 00:42:39,860
Give me the sample dress and I'll let you live.

490
00:42:54,990 --> 00:42:57,660
You guys... really want to withdraw?

491
00:42:57,660 --> 00:43:01,300
Yes, we don't have a sample dress now.

492
00:43:01,300 --> 00:43:04,090
Ruyi Resist Dye Shop's clothing is here!

